*&quot;Fear of Dreaming: The Selected Poems&quot; (Penguin Books; November 1, 1993)
*&quot;Void of Course: Poems 1994–1997&quot; (Penguin Books; October 1, 1998) 
*&quot;8 Fragments for Kurt Cobain&quot; (1994)

