== Party presidents ==
* Stjepan Radić (1904–1928)
* Vladko Maček (1928–1964)
* Juraj Krnjević (1964–1988)
* Josip Torbar (1988–1991)
* Drago Stipac (1991–1994)
* Zlatko Tomčić (1994–2005)
* Josip Friščić (2005–2012)
* Branko Hrg (2012–2016)
* Krešo Beljak (2016–)

